The '''[[Webometrics]] Ranking of Business Schools''',<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://business-schools.webometrics.info/en|title=Welcome to Ranking Web of business {{!}} Ranking Web of business|website=business-schools.webometrics.info|access-date=2017-06-16}}</ref> also known as Ranking Web of Business Schools, is a ranking system for the world's Business Schools based on a composite indicator that takes into account both the volume of the Web contents (number of web pages and files) and the visibility and impact of these web publications according to the number of external inlinks (site citations) they received. The ranking is published by the [[Cybermetrics Lab]], a research group of the [[Spanish National Research Council]] (CSIC) located in Madrid.

This ranking was discontinued in 2013 and is no longer updated.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://business-schools.webometrics.info/en|title=Welcome to Ranking Web of business {{!}} Ranking Web of business|website=business-schools.webometrics.info|access-date=2017-06-16}}</ref>

This discontinued ranking is however often cited (as at 16/6/2017) by google as its main  ranking reference.

Examples are : "Spain business school ranking " = <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.ch/search?q=spain+business+school+ranking&oq=spain+business+school+ranking&gs_l=serp.1.0.0j0i5i30k1l2j0i8i30k1l2.193838.194464.0.196438.5.5.0.0.0.0.80.354.5.5.0....0...1.1.64.serp..0.5.344...0i7i30k1j0i8i7i30k1j0i7i5i30k1.qHo7b4xMOXM|title=spain business school ranking - Google-Suche|last=|first=|date=|website=goo.gl|language=de-CH|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-06-16}}</ref>  "Zurich business school ranking" <ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.google.ch/search?q=zurich+business+school+ranking&oq=zurich+business+school+ranking&gs_l=serp.3..0i7i30k1j0j0i7i30k1j0i5i30k1l2j0i8i30k1.166270.167465.0.168302.6.6.0.0.0.0.104.388.4j1.5.0....0...1.1.64.serp..1.5.388...0i8i7i30k1j0i7i5i30k1.IAj3IJiJF5g|title=zurich business school ranking - Google-Suche|last=|first=|date=|website=goo.gl|language=de-CH|archive-url=|archive-date=|dead-url=|access-date=2017-06-16}}</ref> etc.

The [[Webometrics Ranking of World Universities]] is a similar ranking of universities.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.webometrics.info/en/Europe/Switzerland|title=Switzerland  {{!}} Ranking Web of Universities|website=www.webometrics.info|access-date=2017-06-16}}</ref>

